            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/razers-new-remote-play-tech-will-soon-let-you-stream-your-pc-library-to-your-phone/1100-6528659/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="site-main">

      
                    
  
